extends ui_layout

block content

  .ui.text.container
    br
    h2 Images and Self-Image Post-Activity Quiz
    form#images_post.ui.reply.form(action='/postquiz/image', method='POST')
      input(type='hidden', name='_csrf', value=_csrf)
      .ui.form
        .grouped.fields
          label(for='alter_post') What does "altering a photo" mean?
        .field
          .ui.radio.checkbox
            input.hidden(type='radio', name='alter_post', tabindex='0', value='1')
            label Using a program or app to change the way it looks.
        .field
          .ui.radio.checkbox
            input.hidden(type='radio', name='alter_post', tabindex='0', value='0')
            label Using a lot of hashtags to make it go viral.
        .field
          .ui.radio.checkbox
            input.hidden(type='radio', name='alter_post',  tabindex='0', value='0')
            label Restricting the number of people who can view it.
        .grouped.fields
          label(for='photo_post') What are different ways that an image of someone can be altered?
        .field
          .ui.radio.checkbox
            input.hidden(type='radio', name='photo_post', tabindex='0', value='0')
            label Using makeup and perfect lighting when the photo is taken.
        .field
          .ui.radio.checkbox
            input.hidden(type='radio', name='photo_post', tabindex='0', value='0')
            label Using photoshop to change how the photo looks after it's taken.
        .field
          .ui.radio.checkbox
            input.hidden(type='radio', name='photo_post', tabindex='0', value='0')
            label Using an app to add a filter to the photo. 
        .field
          .ui.radio.checkbox
            input.hidden(type='radio', name='photo_post', tabindex='0', value='1')
            label All of the above. 
        .grouped.fields
          label(for='motivate_post') What are some reasons that people might post an altered photo on social media?
        .field
          .ui.radio.checkbox
            input.hidden(type='radio', name='motivate_post', tabindex='0', value='0')
            label To get likes or comments on a photo.
        .field
          .ui.radio.checkbox
            input.hidden(type='radio', name='motivate_post', tabindex='0', value='0')
            label To make themselves look cooler.
        .field
          .ui.radio.checkbox
            input.hidden(type='radio', name='motivate_post', tabindex='0', value='0')
            label To show everyone their artistic talent.
        .field
          .ui.radio.checkbox
            input.hidden(type='radio', name='motivate_post', tabindex='0', value='0')
            label To promote or sell a product.
        .field
          .ui.radio.checkbox
            input.hidden(type='radio', name='motivate_post', tabindex='0', value='1')
            label All of the above.
        .grouped.fields
          label(for='mislead_post') True or false: Social media is a completely accurate representation of a person's life.
        .field
          .ui.radio.checkbox
            input.hidden(type='radio', name='lie_post', tabindex='0', value='0')
            label True.
        .field
          .ui.radio.checkbox
            input.hidden(type='radio', name='lie_post', tabindex='0', value='1')
            label False.
        .grouped.fields
          label(for='everyone_post') True or false: altering a photo could trick people into believing something that's not true.
        .field
          .ui.radio.checkbox
            input.hidden(type='radio', name='everyone_post', tabindex='0', value='1')
            label True.
        .field
          .ui.radio.checkbox
            input.hidden(type='radio', name='everyone_post', tabindex='0', value='0')
            label False.
  
        br
        h2 Just a few more questions... There are no right or wrong answers here!
        .grouped.fields
          label(for='like') How much did you like this activity?
        .field
          .ui.radio.checkbox
            input.hidden(type='radio', name='like', tabindex='0', value='1')
            label I didn't like it at all.
        .field
          .ui.radio.checkbox
            input.hidden(type='radio', name='like', tabindex='0', value='2')
            label Not very much, but it wasn't awful.
        .field
          .ui.radio.checkbox
            input.hidden(type='radio', name='like', tabindex='0', value='3')
            label A little bit, it was neither good nor bad.
        .field
          .ui.radio.checkbox
            input.hidden(type='radio', name='like', tabindex='0', value='4')
            label Some - it was god but not amazing.
        .field
          .ui.radio.checkbox
            input.hidden(type='radio', name='like', tabindex='0', value='5')
            label A lot - it was awesome!
        .grouped.fields
          label(for='friends') Would you recommend this activity to your friends?
        .field
          .ui.radio.checkbox
            input.hidden(type='radio', name='friends', tabindex='0', value='1')
            label No, not at all.
        .field
          .ui.radio.checkbox
            input.hidden(type='radio', name='friends', tabindex='0', value='2')
            label Maybe.
        .field
          .ui.radio.checkbox
            input.hidden(type='radio', name='friends', tabindex='0', value='3')
            label Yes, I would!
        .grouped.fields
          label(for='length') What did you think of the length of the activity?
        .field
          .ui.radio.checkbox
            input.hidden(type='radio', name='length', tabindex='0', value='1')
            label It was too short.
        .field
          .ui.radio.checkbox
            input.hidden(type='radio', name='length', tabindex='0', value='2')
            label It was just the right length.
        .field
          .ui.radio.checkbox
            input.hidden(type='radio', name='length', tabindex='0', value='3')
            label It was too long.
        .grouped.fields
          label(for='understand') Do you think you understand the issues of images and self-image better after completing the activity?
        .field
          .ui.radio.checkbox
            input.hidden(type='radio', name='understand', tabindex='0', value='1')
            label Yes, I understand the issues better.
        .field
          .ui.radio.checkbox
            input.hidden(type='radio', name='understand', tabindex='0', value='2')
            label I'm not sure.
        .field
          .ui.radio.checkbox
            input.hidden(type='radio', name='understand', tabindex='0', value='3')
            label No, I didn't learn anything.
        button.ui.button(type='submit') Submit
      br
      br
      br
